<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ بِهَذَا اللَّفْظِ لَكِنْ فِي الْحَدِيثِ <span class="c1">" فُضِّلَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ عَلَى الرَّجُلِ بِتِسْعَةٍ وَتِسْعِينَ جُزْءًا مِنَ اللَّذَّةِ وَلَكِنَّ اللَّهَ أَبْقَى عَلَيْهَا الْحَيَاءَ "</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢١٦ - الشَّيْبُ نُورُ الْمُؤْمِنِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ بِهَذَا اللَّفْظِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢١٧ - شَيْبٌ وَعَيْبٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كَلامٌ يُوَبَّخُ بِهِ الشَّيْبُ وَلَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢١٨ - الشَّيْخُ فِي قَوْمِهِ كَالنَّبِيِّ فِي أُمَّتِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>